# PHASE 1: Command Definition

## Define Basic Properties

DECLARE description_text: string
DECLARE argument_hint_text: string

SET description_text = "Brief description shown in /help menu"
SET argument_hint_text = "[arg1] [arg2] [optional-arg]"

## Usage Pattern

```
/command-name arg1 arg2 optional-arg
```

## Argument Access

- `$ARGUMENTS` - Captures all arguments as single string
- `$1` - First positional argument
- `$2` - Second positional argument
- `$3` - Third positional argument
- `@file/path` - Reference file contents
- `!command` - Execute bash command inline

