# PHASE 2: Implementation Instructions

## Your Command Logic Here

WHEN user_invokes_command:
EXTRACT $ARGUMENTS INTO command_input

    IF command_input === null:
        REPORT "No arguments provided"
        EXIT 1

    ## Process arguments
    FOR EACH arg IN $ARGUMENTS:
        ANALYZE arg FOR validity
        IF arg.valid:
            EXECUTE operation WITH arg
        ELSE:
            REPORT "Invalid argument: " + arg

## Using Positional Arguments

IF $1 !== null AND $2 !== null:
EXECUTE structured_operation WITH parameter1: $1, parameter2: $2

    IF $3 !== null:
        EXECUTE optional_operation WITH $3

## File References

WHEN command_references_file:
READ @file/path INTO file_content
ANALYZE file_content FOR target_pattern
REPORT findings

## Bash Command Execution

IF allowed_tools CONTAINS "Bash":
EXECUTE Bash WITH "!command_here" INTO command_output
ANALYZE command_output
REPORT results

