# PHASE 3: Frontmatter Configuration

## Frontmatter Fields Reference

| Field                      | Required | Description                         | Example                      |
| -------------------------- | -------- | ----------------------------------- | ---------------------------- |
| `description`              | No\*     | Brief description                   | "Create a git commit"        |
| `argument-hint`            | No       | Arguments format                    | "[message]"                  |
| `allowed-tools`            | No       | Tools Claude can use (string/list)  | "Bash(git:\*), Read"         |
| `model`                    | No       | Specific model                      | "claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929" |
| `disable-model-invocation` | No       | Hide from SlashCommand tool         | true/false                   |
| `context`                  | No       | Execution context (normal/fork)     | "fork"                       |
| `agent`                    | No       | Agent type for execution            | "general-purpose"            |
| `hooks`                    | No       | Hook definitions (YAML list) v2.1.0 | [{type: PreToolUse}]         |

\*If omitted, first line of content is used as description

