# PHASE 4: Template Creation Workflow

## STEP 1: Copy Template

EXECUTE Bash WITH "cp .claude/commands/commands.template .claude/commands/your-command.md"

## STEP 2: Update Frontmatter

EDIT ".claude/commands/your-command.md" WITH:
old_string: "description: Brief description..."
new_string: "description: Your actual description"

EDIT frontmatter WITH actual values FOR: - description - argument-hint - allowed-tools - model (if specific model needed)

## STEP 3: Write Command Instructions

REPLACE template_instructions WITH actual_command_logic

## STEP 4: Test Command

EXECUTE "/your-command test-arg1 test-arg2"
ANALYZE execution_result
IF errors_found:
DEBUG command_logic
ITERATE TO STEP 3
ELSE:
REPORT "Command working correctly"

## STEP 5: Cleanup

DELETE ".claude/commands/commands.template"

